            <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pay attention to each scenario and the people in it. For each situation, think about the correct form of addressing each other in Spanish.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Look at the pictures and read the short dialogues. Indicate whether each statement is true (&lt;i&gt;cierto&lt;/i&gt;) or false (&lt;i&gt;falso&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="prompt"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECS1/ECS1_U1_UA_GA_Activity1_Q1.jpg" alt="Two girls sitting a table with books open, smiling and giving each other a high five."&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SARITA&lt;/strong&gt;: ¡Hola, Ava! ¿Cómo está usted?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE1]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AVA&lt;/strong&gt;: Estoy muy bien, Sarita. ¿Y tú?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE2]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECS1/ECS1_U1_UA_GA_Activity1_Q2.jpg" alt="A doctor sitting next to an elderly gentleman with a form in his hands."&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SR. MEDINA&lt;/strong&gt;: Buenos días, doctor. ¿Cómo estás?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE3]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DOCTOR&lt;/strong&gt;: Buenos días, señora Medina. Estoy bien. ¿Y usted?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE4]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://cdn.waysidepublishing.com/textbooks/QTI/ECS1/ECS1_U1_UA_GA_Activity1_Q3.jpg" alt="Two young women facing each other with their arms reaching out to one another. The woman facing forward is smiling."&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VIOLETA&lt;/strong&gt;: Hola, Irene. Buenas tardes. ¿Cómo estás?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE5]&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IRENE&lt;/strong&gt;: Hola. Estoy bien. ¿Y usted?&lt;/p&gt;
[RESPONSE6]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</mattext>
